<p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">立，建始也；冬，终也；万物收藏也。</span></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763027979777.png" alt="1763027979777.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763027979777.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">冬已始，天地寒，万物藏；夜渐长，星辰冷，百虫眠。当节气行至立冬，天地便收敛了声响。</span></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763028053576.png" alt="1763028053576.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763028053576.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">此刻，广袤的黑龙江大地，正上演着季节更迭的壮丽景象。兴安岭林海雪原初现，三江平原沃野千里归于宁静，各大水系进入流冰期。</span></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763028079896.png" alt="1763028079896.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763028079896.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">江水墨蓝，宛如巨龙蛰伏，林间丰富的山珍，水中肥美的江鱼，是自然在沉寂之前，给予这片土地的慷慨馈赠。</span></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763028099461.png" alt="1763028099461.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763028099461.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">人们在此收获、储备，以迎接漫长的冬季，江风渐寒，同江街津口的赫哲人，也同样感知着自然的节律。</span></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763028115516.png" alt="1763028115516.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763028115516.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">这片江水环绕的丰饶之地，因得天独厚的自然资源，与历史悠久的渔猎文明，孕育了赫哲族这一“逐江而居，因鱼而兴”的民族。</span></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763028133851.png" alt="1763028133851.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763028133851.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">在未来几个月里，他们将透过封冻的江河，阅读冰层之下流淌的记忆。此刻，这份记忆，正被鞣制进鱼皮里。</span></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763028148416.png" alt="1763028148416.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763028148416.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763028164301.png" alt="1763028164301.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763028164301.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">一部“穿在身上的史诗”，从指尖缓缓显形，由掌心代代传承。</span></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763028187941.png" alt="1763028187941.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763028187941.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763028207081.png" alt="1763028207081.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763028207081.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">一袭鱼皮衣，纳尽三江寒浪，亦缝入了整个部族的呼吸。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763028435361.png" alt="1763028435361.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763028435361.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763028452936.png" alt="1763028452936.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763028452936.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">破冰求鱼，穿针引线。赫哲人用技艺续写着一场与自然的共生不息。赫哲人撒开千张网，船儿满江鱼满舱。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763028494536.png" alt="1763028494536.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763028494536.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763028511576.png" alt="1763028511576.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763028511576.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">立冬过后，收获被储藏，时间的肌理在与技艺的对话中，愈发鲜活。苍凉的吟唱，是穿越风雪的历史回响。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763028536897.png" alt="1763028536897.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763028536897.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">赫哲族鱼皮制作技艺，也是人类的生存艺术。“故事”里的匠魂与匠艺，在这跃动的火光中，完成了一次又一次的交付接力，将创作的星火，悄然点亮。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763028550976.png" alt="1763028550976.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763028550976.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">2006年5月20日，赫哲族鱼皮制作技艺，经国务院批准列入第一批国家级非物质文化遗产名录。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763028569971.png" alt="1763028569971.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763028569971.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">古老的智慧从未冻结，它如冰封下的江流。在新的时代，焕发出新的活力。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763028589016.png" alt="1763028589016.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763028589016.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763028651656.png" alt="1763028651656.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763028651656.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763028668821.png" alt="1763028668821.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763028668821.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">它化作时尚的配饰，化作光影的艺术。这鱼皮上记载的，不再是严寒，而是时间绣下的不朽的年轮。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763028682295.png" alt="1763028682295.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763028682295.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">立冬，藏万物于寂静，而赫哲人，藏热烈于冰。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763028701936.png" alt="1763028701936.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763028701936.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">文化便在这一次次的“立冬”里得以珍藏，藏永恒于蜕变的皮囊。老幼相授，口耳相传。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763028719776.png" alt="1763028719776.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763028719776.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p><br></p>